// Temporary mockup - DELETE after design approval
---
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Modules - A1 Wide Cards</title>
  <style>
    @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Plus+Jakarta+Sans:wght@400;600;700;800&display=swap');

    * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }
    body { font-family: 'Plus Jakarta Sans', sans-serif; background: #f5f0e8; color: #fff; }

    .section-header {
      text-align: center;
      padding: 80px 20px 50px;
    }
    .section-header h2 {
      font-size: 2.5rem;
      font-weight: 800;
      letter-spacing: -0.03em;
      color: #1a1a1a;
      margin-bottom: 12px;
    }
    .section-header h2 span { color: #e74c3c; }
    .section-header p {
      color: rgba(26,26,26,0.5);
      font-size: 1rem;
      max-width: 500px;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }

    .scroll-wrap {
      padding: 0 0 80px;
      overflow: hidden;
    }
    .scroll-track {
      display: flex;
      gap: 24px;
      padding: 0 40px;
      overflow-x: auto;
      scroll-snap-type: x mandatory;
      -webkit-overflow-scrolling: touch;
      scrollbar-width: none;
    }
    .scroll-track::-webkit-scrollbar { display: none; }

    .card {
      flex: 0 0 420px;
      scroll-snap-align: start;
      background: #1a1a1a;
      border-radius: 16px;
      overflow: hidden;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: row;
      min-height: 220px;
      transition: transform 0.3s;
    }
    .card:hover { transform: translateY(-4px); }

    .card-img {
      width: 180px;
      min-width: 180px;
      position: relative;
      overflow: hidden;
    }
    .card-img img {
      width: 100%;
      height: 100%;
      object-fit: cover;
    }
    .card-num {
      position: absolute;
      top: 12px;
      left: 12px;
      background: rgba(0,0,0,0.7);
      color: #e74c3c;
      font-size: 0.7rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      letter-spacing: 0.12em;
      padding: 4px 10px;
      border-radius: 6px;
      text-transform: uppercase;
    }

    .card-body {
      padding: 20px;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      justify-content: center;
    }
    .card-title {
      font-size: 1.05rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: #fff;
      line-height: 1.3;
      margin-bottom: 12px;
    }
    .card-topics { list-style: none; }
    .card-topics li {
      font-size: 0.8rem;
      color: rgba(255,255,255,0.55);
      padding: 2px 0;
    }
    .card-topics li::before { content: '+ '; color: #e74c3c; font-weight: 600; }

    @media (max-width: 768px) {
      .card { flex: 0 0 85vw; flex-direction: column; }
      .card-img { width: 100%; min-width: 100%; height: 180px; }
      .section-header h2 { font-size: 1.8rem; }
      .scroll-track { padding: 0 20px; gap: 16px; }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

  <div class="section-header">
    <h2>What You'll <span>Master</span></h2>
    <p>7 modules. 30+ lessons. Everything you need to nail your low end.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="scroll-wrap">
    <div class="scroll-track">
      <div class="card">
        <div class="card-img">
          <img src="https://uploads.teachablecdn.com/attachments/BauKxvLpQYqLoxR7j01z_low+end+1+copy.jpg" alt="" />
          <div class="card-num">Module 01</div>
        </div>
        <div class="card-body">
          <p class="card-title">Low End Theory - Fine-Tuning the Foundation</p>
          <ul class="card-topics">
            <li>Why Low End Is So Important?</li>
            <li>Why Is It So Hard to Mix?</li>
            <li>FAQ & Common Mistakes</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="card">
        <div class="card-img">
          <img src="https://uploads.teachablecdn.com/attachments/5LOiP0Txl2oQno23I0gW_low+end.jpg" alt="" />
          <div class="card-num">Module 02</div>
        </div>
        <div class="card-body">
          <p class="card-title">Navigating Tools and Challenges</p>
          <ul class="card-topics">
            <li>Your Ears</li>
            <li>Speakers & Room</li>
            <li>Headphones</li>
            <li>Metering</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="card">
        <div class="card-img">
          <img src="https://uploads.teachablecdn.com/attachments/iduxgXajRo6h1LaC7Ahw_dQUY9H3oZvvbU7wsrJUyyvruMXwsYj8G2SdTfqv3+copy.jpg" alt="" />
          <div class="card-num">Module 03</div>
        </div>
        <div class="card-body">
          <p class="card-title">Sound Sculpting - The Perfect Kick</p>
          <ul class="card-topics">
            <li>What Makes a Perfect Kick?</li>
            <li>Kick Shaping (5 Demos)</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="card">
        <div class="card-img">
          <img src="https://uploads.teachablecdn.com/attachments/9GER2ESQpyYJYAdxuM3v_mono.jpg" alt="" />
          <div class="card-num">Module 04</div>
        </div>
        <div class="card-body">
          <p class="card-title">All About The Bass</p>
          <ul class="card-topics">
            <li>Saturation</li>
            <li>Mono-Compatibility</li>
            <li>Creating Wide Bassline</li>
            <li>Note Selection</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="card">
        <div class="card-img">
          <img src="https://uploads.teachablecdn.com/attachments/mQyIVU7NQEbQB6k6p4kA_sidechain.jpg" alt="" />
          <div class="card-num">Module 05</div>
        </div>
        <div class="card-body">
          <p class="card-title">Kick Bass Chemistry</p>
          <ul class="card-topics">
            <li>The Ideal Low End</li>
            <li>Dynamic Phase Rotation</li>
            <li>Low-End Coherence</li>
            <li>Mastering Stage</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="card">
        <div class="card-img">
          <img src="https://uploads.teachablecdn.com/attachments/aq3se6LNQkGTFfZVURXp_genre.jpg" alt="" />
          <div class="card-num">Module 06</div>
        </div>
        <div class="card-body">
          <p class="card-title">Case Studies - Real-Life Examples</p>
          <ul class="card-topics">
            <li>EDM</li>
            <li>Pop / Dance / Funk</li>
            <li>Trap / Hip Hop</li>
            <li>Reggaeton</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="card">
        <div class="card-img">
          <img src="https://uploads.teachablecdn.com/attachments/Q5bGAEPwRXiGHIpphDVS_LOW+END+MASTERY.jpg" alt="" />
          <div class="card-num">Module 07</div>
        </div>
        <div class="card-body">
          <p class="card-title">Bonus Lessons</p>
          <ul class="card-topics">
            <li>Spectre vs RBass</li>
            <li>Working Towards Loudness</li>
            <li>Live Workshop</li>
            <li>Advanced Kick Shaping</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

</body>
</html>
